title: Was I supposed to get honor capsules for level 1-30 since I was level 30 when the season ended?

replies.body:
Those leveling capsules weren't retroactively added to anyone's account since you were able to keep playing at level 30 and gain IP which was converted into BE. 

https://i.gyazo.com/7f6621c6d6623d7e53ca06a2e3f809c1.png
I think you mean the champion capsules. And no, you don't any rewards if you were already level 30 when the season ended.
